  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nCurrently prior to genesis queries for the genesis state will only succeed if made using the `genesis` tag. This causes nodes configured with a checkpoint sync URL to fail, which is a bit annoying.\r\n\r\nThe error is:\r\n\r\n```\r\n> curl \"http://localhost:5052/eth/v2/debug/beacon/states/justified\"\r\n{\"code\":500,\"message\":\"UNHANDLED_ERROR: UnableToReadSlot\",\"stacktraces\":[]}\r\n```\r\n\r\nShould be simple enough to fix.\r\n",
